item.title: Marvin Gaye - What's Going On - Ukulele Play-Alongs!
item.description: Play along video for the song What's Going On by Marvin Gaye from the channel Ukulele Play-Alongs!. Chords used in the song: Am11, B, B9♯5, C♯m7, Emaj7, F♯m.

item.title: Marvin Gaye & Tammi Terrell - Ain't No Mountain High Enough - Key of Am - ukeplayalongs
item.description: Play along video for the song Ain't No Mountain High Enough by Marvin Gaye & Tammi Terrell from the channel ukeplayalongs. Chords used in the song: Am, Am7, D7, Dm, E7, F, G, G7.
